On Sunday morning the Riverview Flats community was thrown into something representing a war zone, when a man wielding a gun ran through in an apparent gang-related hit.The incident, captured on video, happened at around 11 am with kids and families milling outside their homes. In the footage a man can be seen running and firing numerous shots before running away. Towards the end of the video a man in a red hoodie is seen on the floor with a crowd around him. Lieutenant Colonel Andr&egrave; Traut confirmed to City Press that a 24-year-old man was arrested for murder and will make an appearance in the Worcester court on Wednesday.&nbsp;Warning: The footage below is graphic and is not suitable for sensitive viewers